title: The List with Colleen Lopez 10.05.2017 - 10 PM
description:
We're all about shoes tonight on The List featuring Sam Edelman, Minnetonka, Fix-a-Heel, and more! Plus a pre-sell of Rhonda Shear's upcoming Today's Special. Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.

*Prices shown on the previously recorded video may not represent the current price. Visit http://www.hsn.com to view the current selling price. Shop The List on HSN.com!
